STATEMENT_TEXT: SELECT SS_WHOLESALE_COST , SR_NET_LOSS FROM STORE_SALES INNER JOIN STORE_RETURNS ON SR_TICKET_NUMBER = SS_TICKET_NUMBER AND SR_ITEM_SK = SS_ITEM_SK WHERE SS_STORE_SK = 2 AND SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK = 2451680

SELECT Q1.SS_WHOLESALE_COST AS "SS_WHOLESALE_COST", Q2.SR_NET_LOSS AS "SR_NET_LOSS" FROM DB2INST1.STORE_SALES AS Q1, DB2INST1.STORE_RETURNS AS Q2 WHERE (Q2.SR_TICKET_NUMBER = Q1.SS_TICKET_NUMBER) AND (Q2.SR_ITEM_SK = Q1.SS_ITEM_SK) AND (Q2.SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK = 2451680) AND (Q1.SS_STORE_SK = 2)

SELECT CR_RETURNING_ADDR_SK , CS_SALES_PRICE FROM CATALOG_RETURNS INNER JOIN CATALOG_SALES ON CS_ORDER_NUMBER = CR_ORDER_NUMBER AND CS_ITEM_SK = CR_ITEM_SK WHERE CS_NET_PAID <= +68 AND CR_REFUNDED_HDEMO_SK <= 939

SELECT Q1.CR_RETURNING_ADDR_SK AS "CR_RETURNING_ADDR_SK", Q2.CS_SALES_PRICE AS "CS_SALES_PRICE" FROM DB2INST1.CATALOG_RETURNS AS Q1, DB2INST1.CATALOG_SALES AS Q2 WHERE (Q2.CS_ORDER_NUMBER = Q1.CR_ORDER_NUMBER) AND (Q2.CS_ITEM_SK = Q1.CR_ITEM_SK) AND (Q1.CR_REFUNDED_HDEMO_SK <= 939) AND (Q2.CS_NET_PAID <= 68)

SELECT SS_EXT_LIST_PRICE , SR_STORE_CREDIT FROM STORE_SALES INNER JOIN STORE_RETURNS ON SR_CUSTOMER_SK = SS_CUSTOMER_SK AND SR_ITEM_SK = SS_ITEM_SK WHERE SS_ADDR_SK >= 8970 AND SR_CUSTOMER_SK <= 93014

SELECT Q1.SS_EXT_LIST_PRICE AS "SS_EXT_LIST_PRICE", Q2.SR_STORE_CREDIT AS "SR_STORE_CREDIT" FROM DB2INST1.STORE_SALES AS Q1, DB2INST1.STORE_RETURNS AS Q2 WHERE (Q2.SR_CUSTOMER_SK = Q1.SS_CUSTOMER_SK) AND (Q2.SR_ITEM_SK = Q1.SS_ITEM_SK) AND (Q2.SR_CUSTOMER_SK <= 93014) AND (8970 <= Q1.SS_ADDR_SK)
